⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Julie Harbor
node VBL · VBL · ⟦Julie Harbor:VBL:4286eb⟧

WHO   — Julie Harbor — the grounded love interest
WHAT  — The clear eye: the one who has watched football take her brother's knee and the town's good sense, and wants the person, not the position.
WHERE — VBL · Varsity Blues (1999)  Framework inputs: Varsity Blues (1999, dir. Brian Robbins, MTV Films/Paramount); verified cast & facts  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the hero needs someone who already sees what he's learning — that the game is a trap, not a throne.
HOW   — By loving the kid who reads, refusing to be a quarterback's prize, and seeing the cost before he does.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I love the boy who reads, not the quarterback the town is trying to build out of him.

